<li style=3D"direction:ltr">Dr. Hamilton&#39;s annual acoustics community p=
ool party</li><li style=3D"direction:ltr">ME department holiday party</li><=
/ul>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr">Please let me know if you have any questions a=
nd we look forward to hearing from you soon!</div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr"><br>
</div>
<div style=3D"direction:ltr">Sincerely,</div>
